io.ddf.util

Class Utils.ClassMethod

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.ddf.util.Utils.ClassMethod
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    MLClassMethods.PredictMethod, MLClassMethods.TrainMethod
    Enclosing class:
    Utils

    public static class Utils.ClassMethod
extends Object
    Helper class to parse a string of the form className#methodName into an object containing the instantiated object, and a method reference. It can then be used to invoke that method on that instantiated object.
